            <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>énès, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>is, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>is, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
